data.chText: 这一房产或其中任何部分有用于商业活动吗？
data.enText: Is the property or any part thereof used for commercial activity?

tr: of or concerning this or that

value.def: Thereof is used after a noun to relate that noun to a situation or thing that you have just mentioned.

example.ex: ...his belief in God — or the lack thereof.

example.ex: ...a charge of £20 per hour or part thereof.
example.tran: 一小时或不足一小时收费 20 英镑
